dct_description_sm: Includes text, indexed directories, key to bus routes, key to night bus. Publisher's no.: 9. Map of roads accessible by car in Paris. Paris metro map with advice on riding the metro. Indices of suburban buses leaving from Paris, night services, and places to park. List of city buses and advice on riding the bus.
